 I tried to migrate <a href="http://nuwiki.openwrt.org/oldwiki/openwrtdocs/hardware/netgear/wnr854t" class="urlextern" title="http://nuwiki.openwrt.org/oldwiki/openwrtdocs/hardware/netgear/wnr854t"  rel="nofollow">this article</a> as described <a href="migrating" class="urlextern" title="http://wiki.openwrt.org/meta/migrating"  rel="nofollow">here</a>, but failed to find any <strong>admin</strong> on the right. I was logged in. <abbr title="By the way">BTW</abbr>, I don&#039;t like the new template - too much space wasted on the right. <em><a href="mailto:&#x6a;&#x61;&#x6c;&#x32;&#x40;&#x67;&#x6d;&#x78;&#x2e;&#x64;&#x65;" class="mail" title="&#x6a;&#x61;&#x6c;&#x32;&#x40;&#x67;&#x6d;&#x78;&#x2e;&#x64;&#x65;">jal2</a> 2009/08/18</em></div></blockquote>

