<h3 class="sectionedit5" id="divide_table_of_hardware_by_platform_type">Divide Table of Hardware by platform type</h3>
<div class="level3">
<blockquote><div class="no">
 OpenWrt is a deploy system for a lot of different platform, I believe that the new toh should be divided based on platform type. For example not all supported devices are wireless router, hence we should also categorize developer board and phone. What do you think?  — <em><a href="mailto:&#x63;&#x6c;&#x61;&#x75;&#x64;&#x79;&#x75;&#x73;&#x38;&#x34;&#x40;&#x67;&#x6d;&#x61;&#x69;&#x6c;&#x2e;&#x63;&#x6f;&#x6d;" class="mail" title="&#x63;&#x6c;&#x61;&#x75;&#x64;&#x79;&#x75;&#x73;&#x38;&#x34;&#x40;&#x67;&#x6d;&#x61;&#x69;&#x6c;&#x2e;&#x63;&#x6f;&#x6d;">Claudio</a> 2010/01/15 11:30</em></div></blockquote>

