 For example of a minor correction, as a start, I propose that this current article <a href="discussion" class="urlextern" title="http://wiki.openwrt.org/meta/discussion"  rel="nofollow">discussion</a> be renamed to <a href="discussion" class="urlextern" title="http://wiki.openwrt.org/meta/discussion"  rel="nofollow">discussions</a>. — <em><a href="https://forum.openwrt.org/profile.php?id=53265" class="urlextern" title="https://forum.openwrt.org/profile.php?id=53265"  rel="nofollow">XP1</a> 2011/06/05 05:34</em><blockquote><div class="no">
